{"tid":2141584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾志偉分居20年妻朱錫珍病逝　曾寶儀：低調處理","createTime":"2020-08-05T20:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T21:02:27.000Z","uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6735aa87980dfa7d8438797289a814de5a25951","tid":2141584,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200805/5HEJ6PWSQDNIRQJ6YDSGCQSM6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200805%2F5HEJ6PWSQDNIRQJ6YDSGCQSM6U%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=f5d8ca84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200805%2F5HEJ6PWSQDNIRQJ6YDSGCQSM6U%2F&h=053dd74f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200805/5HEJ6PWSQDNIRQJ6YDSGCQSM6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾志偉（左圖）妻子朱錫珍（右圖左）傳周一過世。香港《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n67歲香港影壇大哥曾志偉與寶媽離婚後，與現任妻子朱錫珍育有2子曾國祥和曾國猷。今年初朱錫珍被拍到因病返港檢查，5月導演曾國祥又被目擊多次進出醫院，顯見母親病情不樂觀。今傳出朱錫珍已於本周一（3日）過世。 對此，《蘋果新聞網》求證曾寶儀經紀人，曾寶儀經紀人表示，她遵照曾國祥的意思，低調處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出版時間：20:52<br />\n更新時間：22:02"},{"pid":"291cc090417b420abb3f08d631000248fa9c603f","tid":2141584,"uid":192465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:26:22.000Z","msg":"人渣賣港賊"},{"pid":"338a6272b4ff9810d3d09163754758c9785b9c94","tid":2141584,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T20:26:28.000Z","msg":"係咪鴛鴦蝴蝶命先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083655a89ee8fc5bdf7f912f32c78291666e8072","tid":2141584,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T21:02:27.000Z","msg":"影壇大哥曾志偉"}]}